(41, 4, 15, 42, 8, 12, 12, 'Satan cometh immediately, and taketh away', 'Connection of the Sower''s Parable', 'Both passages emphasize the role of the devil in taking away the word from those who hear it. This connection highlights the immediate spiritual danger faced by individuals who receive the message but do not believe.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
